divs: Sighting DetailsIam not really sure what I witness,but It was not a plane...I was driving on m-15 going south....I was about 5 min from the city of ortinville when this object flew from east to west tree top level it cast a shadow when it went across the road it bothers me to this day that I have not a clue what it was...I looked in direction that it went and it was gone....It flew to fast to see what it was....I would like to talk to a field investigater if that is all possable....
